<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#ServiceRelatedConsequence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Service Related Consequence"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#ServiceRelatedConsequence> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <https://w3id.org/dpv#Impact> .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#ServiceRelatedConsequence> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A consequence that affects an individual's or organisation's access to or participation in a service"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#ServiceRelatedConsequence> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Service Related Consequence"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#ServiceRelatedConsequence> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Parent term for service-related consequences"@en .
