<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#dpv-MonitoringIndividuals> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Monitoring of humans (as individuals or as groups) which includes a systematic observation or surveillance of behaviour, movements, or activities"@en .
