<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#dpv-NonDataSubjectDataSource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <https://w3id.org/dpv#DataSource> .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#dpv-NonDataSubjectDataSource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Personal data obtained from a third party or another source rather than directly from the individual concerned, especially in cases where informing the data subject would be difficult or impossible, such as in law enforcement, research, or archival processing"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#dpv-NonDataSubjectDataSource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "C25" .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#dpv-NonDataSubjectDataSource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Non Data Subject Data Source"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#dpv-NonDataSubjectDataSource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Existing non-data subject sources in DPV should be moved below this concept"@en .
