<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#eu-aiact-FacialRecognitionTechnology> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A biometric identification system that detects, captures, and compares facial features to identify or verify individuals in real-time or retrospectively, as defined in the EU AI Act"@en .
