<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#eu-gdpr-DPIANotRequiredProcess> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A personal data processing activity that does not require a DPIA according to the whitelists of processing activities published by Member State Data Protection Authorities"@en .
