<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#eu-gdpr-Systematic> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Indication that processing occurs according to a system; is pre-arranged, organised or methodical, and takes place as part of a general plan or is carried out as part of a strategy"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#eu-gdpr-Systematic> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "C29, C39, C45, C51, C50, C55, C82, C89" .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#eu-gdpr-Systematic> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Systematic"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#eu-gdpr-Systematic> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Definition follows ICO UK. Proposed as subclass of eu-gdpr:Systematicity"@en .
