<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#loc-OnPublicRoad> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Any location accessible to the general public, particularly roads and streets used by public or private transportation, where monitoring or control of individuals is conducted via processing operations such as video surveillance or traffic sensors"@en .
