<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Competency> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#SourcePL> .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Competency> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Competency"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Competency> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <https://w3id.org/dpv/pd#External> .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Competency> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Personal data used in the systematic evaluation of an individual's overall effectiveness in applying knowledge and skills, including professional qualifications, behavioural performance, and domain-specific expertise"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Competency> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "C45" .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Competency> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Competency"@en .
