<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Conduct> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A pattern or instance of individual behaviour, particularly in relation to lawfulness, ethics, professional standards, or social expectations. Conduct can be evaluated as good or bad based on its alignment with normative, legal, or reputational frameworks"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Conduct> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Conduct"@en .
<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-Conduct> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The parent for bad conduct and good conduct"@en .
