<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#pd-LocationDisplacement> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Personal data processed to analyse or predict a person's change in location, movement patterns, or relocation behaviours, often linked to economic or social factors"@en .
